title: Secondary User "Back Up" is Unavailable for Android for Pixel 3
content:
I have a new Pixel 5 and I would like to transfer from my existing Pixel 3a my Primary (Personal) and Secondary (Work) accounts. 

However, I can back up my Primary (Personal) account and I cannot back up my Secondary (Work) account. How do I back up my Secondary Work account?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 3a
